\",FontWeight->\"Bold\"]\)\!\(\*StyleBox[\"biii\",FontWeight->\"Bold\"]\): \
\[CapitalBeta](r) = 1, \[GothicCapitalC](r) = 1. \>\"", "]"}], ";", 
