another solution. In this case, we \
\!\(\*StyleBox[\"do\",FontSlant->\"Italic\"]\) obtain a new solution. We are \
re-doing Case d with the assumption that \[ScriptCapitalA](t) = 1; i.e., \
A(t,r) = \[ScriptCapitalA](t) \[CapitalAlpha](r) = \[CapitalAlpha](r).\>\"", 
     "]"}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
