  RowBox[{"\<\"     \\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(11\\)]\\)-2\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(44\\)]\\):  \"\>", "\[InvisibleSpace]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"-", 
     FractionBox[
      RowBox[{"2", " ", 
       SuperscriptBox[
        OverscriptBox["a", "."], "2"]}], 
      SuperscriptBox["a", "2"]]}], "-", 
    FractionBox[
     OverscriptBox["a", "\[DoubleDot]"], "a"], "+", 
    FractionBox[
     SuperscriptBox[
      RowBox[{"(", 
       SuperscriptBox[
        SubscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "4"], "\[Prime]",
        MultilineFunction->None], ")"}], "2"], 
     RowBox[{"2", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", 
      SubsuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "4", "2"]}]]}], 
   "\[InvisibleSpace]", "\<\" = \"\>", "\[InvisibleSpace]", 
   RowBox[{"-", "\[CapitalLambda]"}]}],
  SequenceForm[
