\(44\)]\):  ", (-2) $CellContext`a^(-2) 
    OverDot[$CellContext`a, 1]^2 - $CellContext`a^(-1) 
   OverDot[$CellContext`a, 2] + 
   Rational[1, 2] $CellContext`a^(-2) 
    Subscript[$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD], 4]^(-2) Derivative[1][
