\), \(4\)]\)(r) = a[t\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(]\), \(2\)]\)", E^
   PlusMinus[
    Complex[0, 4] 
     3^Rational[-1, 
        2] $CellContext`r ($CellContext`\[Alpha] $CellContext`\[Beta] \
