Cell[BoxData["\<\"As for Case d_I\[Alpha], a(t) is constant. In order for the \
Solution 2 a(t) to be constant, we would have to have \[CapitalLambda]=0 \
\[Implies] \[DoubleStruckCapitalC](t,r) is undefined. So, Case d_I\[Alpha] is \
not a special case of Solution 2. And, clearly the Case d_I\[Alpha] constant \
