Cell[BoxData["\<\"In viewing all four solutions together (Cases d and d_I\
\[Alpha] and Solutions 1 and 2), we observe they are similar. All have the \
same B and \[DoubleStruckCapitalC], and essentially the same \
\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(\[GothicCapitalD]\\), \\(4\\)]\\). They only differ \
in a(t) and/or A(t,r).\"\>"], "Print",
